'''希氏蹼麝鼩'''（''Nesiotites hidalgo''）是[[歐洲|歐洲]]一種已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[鼩鼱|鼩鼱]]。滅絕前分佈於[[巴利阿里群島|巴利阿里群島]]的[[馬略卡島|馬略卡島]]以及[[梅诺卡岛|梅诺卡岛]]。希氏蹼麝鼩的歷史可以追溯到自晚中新世至早上新世時期，而且其歷史至少有500万年<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Moncunill-Solé|first1=Blanca|last2=Jordana|first2=Xavier|last3=Köhler|first3=Meike|date=September 2016|title=How common is gigantism in insular fossil shrews? Examining the 'Island Rule' in soricids (Mammalia: Soricomorpha) from Mediterranean Islands using new body mass estimation models|url=https://academic.oup.com/zoolinnean/article-lookup/doi/10.1111/zoj.12399|journal=Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society|language=en|volume=178|issue=1|pages=163–182|doi=10.1111/zoj.12399|doi-access=free}}</ref>。
